%2Fbiden-prepares-reject-us-steel-deal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Fb8427273-7ee7-48de-af1e-3a972e5a0fcf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Financial%20Times.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Financial%20Times%20reported%20that%20the%20president%20would%20reject%20the%20deal%20%E2%80%94%20which%20both%20companies%20agreed%20to%20in%20December%20%E2%80%94%20based%20on%20national%20security%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20possible%20acquisition%20of%20a%20once-mighty%20American%20brand%20like%20US%20Steel%20by%20foreign%20investors%20has%20become%20a%20flash%20point%20in%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20with%20both%20major%20candidates%20arguing%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20joint%20campaign%20stop%20with%20Biden%20in%20Pennsylvania%20on%20Monday%2C%20Harris%20told%20supporters%20that%20%26quot%3BUS%20Steel%20should%20remain%20American-owned%20and%20American-operated%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fharris-biden-election-2024-afd4b7fbd9d747e307a8fb5c1f60d5fa%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Associated%20Press%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20also%20repeatedly%20pledged%20to%20block%20the%20sale%20%26quot%3Binstantaneously%26quot%3B%20if%20he%20re-enters%20the%20White%20House%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F01%2F31%2Ftrump-us-steel-sale-00138910%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPolitico%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20stop%20Japan%20from%20buying%20United%20States%20Steel%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20reiterated%20at%20a%20Pennsylvania%20rally%20in%20August%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcommodities%2Ftrump-reiterate-he-will-stop-us-steel-sale-nippon-2024-08-19%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThey%20shouldn't%20be%20all