%3E%20head%20of%20global%20safety%2C%20Antigone%20Davis%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabout.fb.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F11%2Fonline-teen-safety-legislation-is-needed%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublished%20a%20blog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20urging%20government%20regulation%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20children%20and%20teens%20accessing%20Instagram%20and%20other%20social%20media.%20She%20proposed%20that%20Apple%20and%20Google%20take%20charge%20of%20age-gating%20and%20getting%20parental%20consent%20through%20their%20app%20stores.%20She%20wrote%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EParents%20should%20approve%20their%20teen's%20app%20downloads%2C%20and%20we%20support%20federal%20legislation%20that%20requires%20app%20stores%20to%20get%20parents'%20approval%20whenever%20their%20teens%20under%2016%20download%20apps.%20With%20this%20solution%2C%20when%20a%20teen%20wants%20to%20download%20an%20app%2C%20app%20stores%20would%20be%20required%20to%20notify%20their%20parents%2C%20much%20like%20when%20parents%20are%20notified%20if%20their%20teen%20attempts%20to%20make%20a%20purchase.%20Parents%20can%20decide%20if%20they%20want%20to%20approve%20the%20download.%20They%20can%20also%20verify%20the%20age%20of%20their%20teen%20when%20setting%20up%20their%20phone%2C%20negating%20the%20need%20for%20everyone%20to%20verify%20their%20age%20multiple%20times%20across%20multiple%20apps.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20sounds%20like%20Meta%20is%20just%20trying%20to%20wiggle%20out%20of%20having%20to%20clean%20up%20its%20own%20mess.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Meta%20does%20have%20a%20point%3A%20It%20%3Cem%3Ewould%3C%2Fem%3E%20be%20a%20lot%20easier%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Google%20to%20implement%20age-gating%20at%20the%20app-store%20level%20versus%20leaving%20this%20work%20to%20each%20individual%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Ftech%2Fapple-helped-nix-part-of-a-child-safety-bill-more-fights-are-expected-23905d4d%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week%20from%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%2C%20Apple%20is%20not%20at%20all%20willing%20to%20entertain%20this%20idea.%20When%20state%20legislators%20in%20Louisiana%20were%20considering%20a%20bill%20that%20would%20make%20app%20stores%20responsible%20for%20age%20verification%2C%20Apple%20sent%20out%20a%20team%20of%20lobbyists%20to%20help%20shut%20it%20down.%20It%20worked%20%E2%80%94%20that%20part%20of%20the%20bill%20was%20dropped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20new%20wrinkle%20in%20a%20low-key%20feud%20between%20Meta%20and%20Apple.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-blames-apple-10-billion-loss-ad-privacy-warning-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%20resents%20Apple%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20several%20reasons%3A%20Apple%20hurt%20its%20ad%20business%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Bask%20app%20not%20to%20track%26quot%3B%20feature%3B%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-app-store%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApp%20Store%3C%2Fa%3E%20takes%20an%20onerous%20cut%20of%20up%20to%2030%25%20for%20some%20in-app%20purchases%3B%20and%2C%20worst%20of%20all%2C%20Apple%20gets%20away%20with%20a%20smarmy%2C%20holier-than-thou%20attitude%20about%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20might%20imagine%20why%20Apple%20isn't%20excited%20to%20jump%20forward%20with%20a%20plan%20to%20be%20responsible%20for%20age-gating%20all%20social%20apps.%20Apple%20doesn't%20want%20to%20handle%20age%20verification%2C%20because%20that's%20a%20privacy%20nightmare.%20And%20it%20likely%20resents%20having%20to%20clean%20up%20Meta's%20and%20TikTok's%20messes.%20Plus%2C%20Apple%20already%20has%20parental%20controls%20and%20age%20ratings%20in%20the%20App%20Store%20that%20allow%20parents%20to%20block%20apps%20rated%20over%20a%20certain%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20Apple%20and%20Meta