%20can%20be%20a%20pain%20to%20remove%20and%20must%20be%20properly%20attached%20to%20maintain%20waterproof%20sealing%20%E2%80%94%20not%20something%20you%20want%20to%20fuss%20with%20while%20on%20a%20bike%20ride%20or%20snowboard.%20But%20what's%20impressive%20is%20a%20sensor%20that%20lets%20the%20Hero%2013%20Black%20detect%20which%20lens%20is%20attached%2C%20which%20then%20automatically%20adjusts%20the%20settings%20to%20fit%20that%20lens.%20This%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20set%20up%20and%20go%20quickly%2C%20but%20advanced%20users%20can%20tweak%20the%20settings%20further.%20(The%20older%20Max%20Lens%20Mod%20lacks%20this%20handshake%20feature%2C%20so%20it%20isn't%20entirely%20compatible%20with%20the%20Hero%2013%20Black%20without%20manual%20settings%20adjustment.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lenses%20give%20your%20shots%20a%20more%20natural%20look%20than%20a%20digital%20lens%2C%20and%20they%20let%20you%20add%20creative%20touches.%20The%20Anamorphic%20Lens%20Mod%20was%20unavailable%20during%20initial%20testing%2C%20but%20we%20love%20the%20Macro%20Lens%20Mod%20for%20close-up%20shots%20with%20great%20focus%20and%20for%20creating%20depth%20of%20field.%20If%20technically%20possible%2C%20we%20would%20love%20to%20see%20a%20telephoto%20option%20in%20the%20near%20future%2C%20as%20that's%20a%20lens%20we%20think%20many%20users%20would%20appreciate.%20As%20we%20test%20the%20lenses%20further%20for%20a%20full%20review%2C%20we%20will%20have%20a%20more%20in-depth%20analysis%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20these%20Lens%20Mods%20are%20sold%20separately%3B%20we%20don't%20think%20they%20are%20a%20must-have%20for%20most%20people.%20However%2C%20these%20lenses%20are%20worth%20considering%20if%20you'd%20like%20to%20give%20your%20videos%20and%20photos%20a%20unique%20look%20or%20just%20give%20yourself%20some%20options%20when%20shooting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Battery%2C%20accessories%20mount%2C%20GPS%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELonger%20battery%20life%2C%20magnetic%20mount%2C%20and%20the%20return%20of%20GPS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Hero%2013%20Black%20uses%20a%20new%201%2C900mAh%20battery%2C%20compared%20to%20the%201%2C720mAh%20battery%20of%20the%20Hero%2012%20Black.%20GoPro%20claims%20it%20can%20provide%201.5%20hours%20of%20battery%20life%20when%20shooting%20in%204K%20or%205K%20at%2030%20frames%20per%20second%20(fps)%20and%202.5%20hours%20in%201080p%20at%2030%20fps.%20The%20downside%20is%20that%20you%20can't%20use%20the%20battery%20from%20older%20cameras%20(the%20Hero%2012%20Black%2C%20Hero%2011%20Black%2C%20and%20Hero%2010%20Black%20used%20the%20same%20battery%20size)%2C%20but%20on%20the%20upside%2C%20it%20improves%20battery%20life%20%E2%80%94%20a%20big%20issue%20with%20action%20cameras.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20our%20real-world%20observations%2C%20we%20noticed%20we%20could%20shoot%20longer.%20After%20an%20hour%20of%20on-and-off%20continuous%20shooting%2C%20we%20still%20had%20about%2020%25%20battery%20life%20left.%20We%20will%20have%20a%20better%20analysis%20after%20a%20run-down%20test%2C%20but%20GoPro's%20claim%20is%20valid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoPro%20announced%20a%20new%20magnetic%20charging%20option%20called%20the%20Contacto%20Magnetic%20Door%20and%20Power%20Cable%20Kit%20(%2480).%20We%20couldn't%20test%20this%20product%20at%20launch%2C%20but%20it%20allows%20for%20continuous%20power%20without%20removing%20the%20battery%20door.%20This%20maintains%20its%20waterproofing%20and%20dust%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20image%20of%20the%20new%20GoPro%20Contacto%20magnetic%20charging%20system%20with%20and%20without%20cable%20attached.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d89185289b805d1db42c10%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EContacto%20is%20a%20new%20magnetic%20charging%20system%20that%20lets%20your%20recharge%20without%20opening%20the%20battery%20door.%20It's%20waterproof%2C%20so%20it%20can%20be%20used%20underwater%20while%20charging%20continuously.%3Cp%3ELes%20Shu%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBorrowing%20a%20page%20from%20DJI's%20Action%20Camera%20book%2C%20GoPro%20is%20incorporating%20a%20magnetic%20mount%20in%20addition%20to%20its%20mounting%20fingers.%20The%20Magnetic%20Latch%20(%2425)%20lets%20you%20easily%20switch%20between%20often-used%20accessories%20without%20the%20need%20to%20constantly%20remove%20the%20screw.%20The%20Magnetic%20Latch%20isn't%20cheap%20(there's%20also%20a%20Ball%20Joint%20Mount%20for%20%2440)%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20godsend%20for%20anybody%20who%20uses%20different%20mounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20GoPro%20Hero%2013%20Black%20with%20a%20new%20magnetic%20mounting%20system%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d8994f1d8d2deb96b8ce41%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Hero%2013%20Black%20supports%20a%20new%20magnetic%20mounting%20system%20that%20lets%20you%20quickly%20and%20easily%20swap%20accessories.%3Cp%3EGoPro%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20user%20requests%2C%20GoPro%20is%20bringing%20back%20GPS%20tracking%20and%20geotagging%2C%20which%20were%20removed%20from%20the%20Hero%2012%20Black.%20You%20can%20record%20speed%2C%20path%2C%20terrain%2C%20altitude%2C%20and%20g-force%20and%20overlay%20this%20information%20over%20your%20video%20in%20the%20form%20of%20stickers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Pro-level%20features%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPro-level%20features%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20image%20of%20the%20GoPro%20Hero%2013%20Black%20screen%20with%20advanced%20settings%20menu%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d89c051d8d2deb96b8d0cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAs%20with%20previous%20Hero%20Black%20cameras%2C%20the%20Hero%2013%20Black%20has%20pro-level%20settings.%3Cp%3ELes%20Shu%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%20box%2C%20the%20Hero%2013%20Black%20is%20designed%20to%20be%20used%20by%20anyone%2C%20thanks%20to%20an%20easy-to-use%20menu.%20But%20switch%20to%20its%20pro%20mode%2C%20and%20you%20can%20fine-tune%20various%20settings%20to%20your%20liking.%20This%2C%20and%20its%20size%2C%20has%20made%20it%20popular%20among%20professional%20and%20amateur%20filmmakers.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20HB%20lenses%2C%20the%20Hero%2013%20Black%20supports%20Hybrid%20Log%20Gamma%20(HLG)%20HDR%20Video%2C%20finer%20audio%20tuning%2C%20and%20even%20slower%20motion%20at%20up%20to%20400%20fps%20at%20720p.%20And%2C%20the%20Hero%2013%20Black%20supports%20faster%20wireless%20transfers%20using%20WiFi%206%20protocol.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22A%20new%20small%20Hero%20camera%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20new%20small%20Hero%20camera%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-by-side%20image%20of%20the%20GoPro%20Hero%20camera%2C%20showing%20the%20front%20with%20lens%20and%20back%20with%20display.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d88a7114a5cd1fcc8d36c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Hero%20is%20GoPro's%20newest%20and%20smallest%20camera%20with%20a%20rear%20display.%20It%20can%20shoot%20up%20to%204K%2C%20but%20it's%20basic%20compared%20to%20the%20Hero%20Black%20series.%3Cp%3ELes%20Shu%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlongside%20the%20Hero%2013%20Black%20launch%20is%20the%20Hero%20camera.%20Tiny%20cameras%20aren't%20new%20for%20GoPro%20%E2%80%94%20there%20was%20the%20Hero%20Session%20in%20the%20past%20and%20the%20more%20recent%20Hero%2011%20Black%20Mini.%20But%20the%20Hero%20is%20touted%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bsmallest%2C%20lightest%2C%20simplest%20to%20use%2C%20and%20lowest