%20stocks%20lower%20by%20about%2010%25%20within%20the%20next%20few%20weeks%2C%20according%20to%20Renaissance%20Macro%20Research%20founder%20and%20technical%20strategist%20Jeff%20DeGraaf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2Fvideo%2F2024%2F09%2F04%2Ftechnicals-to-watch-in-september.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20interview%20with%20CNBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20DeGraaf%20said%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fnasdaq_100%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENasdaq%20100%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20trade%20to%2017%2C000%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-stock-price-outlook-technical-analysts-eye-danger-zone-levels-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20key%20technical%20level%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20is%20monitoring%20which%20represents%2010%25%20downside%20from%20current%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20DeGraaf%20is%20closely%20watching%20the%20early%20August%20low%20of%205%2C120%20for%20a%20potential%20retest%20of%20support.%20That%20level%20represents%20about%207%25%20downside%20from%20current%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeGraaf%20is%20concerned%20that%20sentiment%20remains%20in%20bullish%20territory%2C%20which%20isn't%20typically%20seen%20when%20the%20market%20is%20at%20or%20near%20a%20bottom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20look%20at%20where%20the%20sentiment%20is%20in%20terms%20of%20small%20speculators%20on%20the%20NDX%20futures%2C%20they're%20still%20very%20very%20net%20long.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20they've%20been%20using%20this%20weakness%20as%20a%20buying%20opportunity.%20And%20that's%20not%20usually%20the%20right%20behavior%20to%20create%20some%20kind%20of%20low%2C%26quot%3B%20DeGraaf%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20is%20about%203%25%20below%20its%20record%20high%2C%20while%20the%20Nasdaq%20100%20is%20down%20about%208%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bullish%20sentiment%20among%20traders%20is%20also%20contrasted%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20September%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-september-season-fed-cuts-election-investing-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20historically%20been%20a%20bad%20month%20for%20stocks.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20DeGraaf%20said%20that%20technology%20stocks%2C%20which%20have%20been%20leading%20the%20market%20higher%20since%20the%20bull%20market%20started%20in%20October%202022%2C%20typically%20underperform%20in%20the%20three%20months%20following%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseptember-fed-interest-rate-cuts-soft-landing-inflation-powell-su-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFederal%20Reserve's%20first%20interest%20rate%20cut.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20look%20particularly%20at%20technology%2C%20it%20does%20not%20fare%20well%20after%20the%20first%20rate%20cut.%20It's%20very%20pro-cyclical%2C%20cyclicals%20tend%20to%20underperform%20for%20at%20least%20three%20months%20after%20the%20first%20Fed%20rate%20cut%2C%26quot%3B%20DeGraaf%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20even%20though%20it%20feels%20like%20the%20calvary%20is%20on%20the%20way%20and%20good%20things%20are%20likely%20to%20happen%2C%20the%20data%20probably%20continues%20to%20be%20weaker%20and%20I%20think%20that's%20one%20of%20the%20things%20that's%20kind%20of%20piling%20up%20on%20us%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20to%20how%20the%20decline%20plays%20out%2C%20DeGraaf%20said%20there%20could%20be%20further%20weakness%20toward%20the%20end%20of%20September%2C%20spilling%20over%20into%20early%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20decline%20would%20create%20a%20two-month%20window%20of%20stocks%20seeing%20little%20movement%2C%20which%20can%20%26quot%3Bbecome%20pretty%20disheartening%20for%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20DeGraaf%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20potential%20decline%20could%20come%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20quick%20flush%20of%20positioning%20among%20trend%20followers%20and%20%26quot%3Bsheer%20panic%26quot%3B%20among%20investors%2C%20similar%20to%20what%20happened%20in%20early%20August%20amid%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-crash-yen-carry-trade-unwind-fed-japan-rates-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyen%20carry%20trade%20blowup.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20one%20of%20those%20two%20things%20happens%2C%20DeGraaf%20sees%20short-term%20stock%20market%20risks%20skewed%20to%20the%20downside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNeither%20one%20of%20those%20have%20we%20seen%20yet%20and%20that's%20why%20we%20think%20there's%20still%20a%20little%20longer%20fuse%20on%20this%20correction%20that's%20likely%20to%20take%20place%20before%20we're%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20DeGraaf%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-correction-early-october-bearish-trifecta-rate-cuts-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725478664000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d8b6e71d8d2deb96b8f130%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-correction-early-october-bearish-trifecta-rate-cuts-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThere's%20still%20a%20little%20longer%20fuse%20on%20this%20correction%20that's%20likely%20to%20take%20place%20before%20we're%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20Renaissance%20Macro's%20Jeff%20DeGraaf%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A145%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-correction-early-october-bearish-trifecta-ra