n%3Cp%3EABC%20News%20quoted%20a%20witness%2C%20student%20Sergio%20Caldera%2C%20as%20saying%20he%20was%20in%20chemistry%20class%20when%20he%20heard%20gunshots.%20Caldera%2C%2017%2C%20told%20ABC%20his%20teacher%20opened%20the%20door%20and%20another%20teacher%20ran%20in%20to%20tell%20her%20to%20shut%20the%20door%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20there's%20an%20active%20shooter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20students%20and%20teachers%20huddled%20in%20the%20room%2C%20someone%20pounded%20on%20his%20classroom%20door%20and%20shouted%20several%20times%20for%20it%20to%20be%20opened.%20When%20the%20knocking%20stopped%2C%20Caldera%20heard%20more%20gunshots%20and%20screams.%20He%20said%20his%20class%20later%20evacuated%20to%20the%20school's%20football%20field%2C%20reported%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20see%20behind%20us%20is%20an%20evil%20thing%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Sheriff%20Jud%20Smith%20said%20during%20a%20brief%20news%20conference%20on%20school%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeorgia%20Governor%20Brian%20Kemp%20said%20on%20social%20media%20website%20X%20that%20state%20agencies%20were%20responding%20to%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20had%20been%20briefed%20on%20the%20shooting%20%26quot%3Band%20his%20administration%20will%20continue%20coordinating%20with%20federal%2C%20state%2C%20and%20local%20officials%20as%20we%20receive%20more%20information.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20U.S.%20has%20seen%20hundreds%20of%20shootings%20inside%20of%20schools%20and%20colleges%20in%20the%20past%20two%20decades%2C%20with%20the%20deadliest%20resulting%20in%20over%2030%20deaths%20at%20Virginia%20Tech%20in%202007.%20The%20carnage%20has%20sparked%20pitched%20debate%20over%20the%20U.S.%20gun%20laws%20and%20the%20U.S.%20Constitution's%20Second%20Amendment%2C%20which%20enshrines%20the%20right%20%26quot%3Bto%20keep%20and%20bear%20arms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E(Inputs%20from%20AFP%20and%20Reuters)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725476100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F1qr42hno_school-shooting_625x300_04_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgunfire-reported-at-high-school-in-us-georgia-currently-under-hard-lockdown-news-agency-afp-6491595%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%20four%20people%20have%20died%20after%20a%20gunman%20opened%20fire%20at%20a%20high%20school%20in%20US's%20Georgia.%20Police%20and%20medics%20rushed%20to%20the%20school%20and%20the%20neighbourhood%20was%20put%20under%20%26quot%3Ba%20hard%20lockdown%26quot%3B.%20The%20suspect%20is%20now%20arrested.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Joker%3A%20Folie%20a%20Deux'%20Early%20Reviews%3A%20Mixed%20reactions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725476052000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113073172%2Cimgsize-66144.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fjoker-folie-a-deux-early-reviews-joaquin-phoenix-and-lady-gaga-starrer-opens-to-mixed-reactions-hailed-as-movie-of-the-year-while-others-call-it-pointless%2Farticleshow%2F113072909.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113072909.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ELady%20Gaga%20and%20Joaquin%20Phoenix%20star%20in%20'Joker%3A%20Folie%20a%20Deux%2C'%20which%20premiered%20at%20the%20Venice%20Film%20Festival.%20Directed%20by%20Todd%20Phillips%2C%20the%20film%20has%20received%20mixed%20reviews%3B%20some%20praise%20its%20performances%20and%20musical%20approach%20while%20others%20criticize%20it%20as%20a%20lackluster%20sequel.%20Despite%20divided%20