pending%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Indian%20Forest%20Service%20officer%20Rahul%20has%20disciplinary%20proceedings%20pending%20against%20him.%20Senior%20advocate%20ANS%20Nadkarni%2C%20who%20represented%20the%20state%2C%20said%20the%20officer%20is%20being%20targeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20that%20the%20noting%20had%20said%20the%20officer%20should%20not%20be%20posted%20at%20the%20Rajaji%20Tiger%20Reserve%2C%20the%20court%20said%20the%20chief%20minister%20%26quot%3Bjust%20ignores%20it%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appointment%20of%20Indian%20Forest%20Service%20officer%20Rahul%2C%20a%20former%20director%20of%20the%20Corbett%20Tiger%20Reserve%2C%20as%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Rajaji%20Tiger%20Reserve%20was%20severely%20discouraged%20by%20senior%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20observed%20that%20there%20was%20a%20specific%20noting%20from%20the%20first%20officer.%20This%20was%20endorsed%20by%20the%20deputy%20secretary%2C%20the%20principal%20secretary%20and%20the%20state's%20forest%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20disagree%20right%20from%20the%20desk%20officer%2C%20the%20deputy%20secretary%2C%20the%20principal%20secretary%2C%20the%20minister%2C%20then%20the%20least%20that%20is%20expected%20is%20that%20there%20is%20some%20application%20of%20mind%20as%20to%20why%20he%20is%20disagreeing%20with%20the%20proposal%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20cannot%20sacrifice%20a%20good%20officer%20against%20whom%20there%20is%20nothing%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nadkarni%20had%20argued.%20%26quot%3BIf%20there%20is%20nothing%2C%20then%20why%20are%20you%20holding%20departmental%20proceedings%20against%20him%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20asked.%20Unless%20there%20is%20some%20prima%20facie%20material%2C%20departmental%20proceedings%20are%20not%20initiated%20against%20anyone%2C%20the%20judges%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725473160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2