0alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fmaj1otq8_suspected-kuki-insurgents_625x300_03_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20the%20remote-controlled%20small%20flying%20device%20as%20a%20weapon%20was%20first%20noticed%20in%20Manipur%20on%20Sunday%20in%20Koutruk%20village%20in%20Imphal%20West%20district.%20In%20the%20attack%20in%20which%20guns%20were%20also%20used%2C%20two%20persons%20were%20killed%20and%20nine%20others%20were%20injured.%20Drones%20were%20employed%20again%20in%20Senjam%20Chirang%2C%20around%203%20km%20away%2C%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20has%20described%20the%20dropping%20of%20bombs%20on%20the%20civilian%20population%20and%20security%20forces%20using%20drones%20as%20an%20act%20of%20terrorism.%20The%20state%20government%20has%20imposed%20restrictions%20on%20the%20import%20of%20drones%20or%20their%20components.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20became%20concerned%20when%20we%20heard%20the%20buzzing%20sound%20of%20drones%20on%20Sunday.%20We%20also%20heard%20that%20bombs%20were%20dropped%20at%20Koutruk.%20Our%20village%20became%20the%20target%20the%20next%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gambhir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20elderly%20farmer%20told%20PTI%20that%20he%20initially%20thought%20the%20buzz%20was%20coming%20from%20random%20drones%20checking%20residential%20localities%20as%20Senjam%20Chirang%20had%20seen%20several%20gunfights%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20within%20seconds%2C%20we%20heard%20a%20loud%20explosion.%20I%20along%20with%20my%20son%20rushed%20outside%20in%20the%20courtyard%20and%20saw%20smoke%20billowing%20from%20the%20cow%20shed.%20The%20second%20bomb%20broke%20the%20roof%20of%20our%20bedroom%20where%20my%20daughter%20was%20and%20she%20was%20injured%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20ran%20towards%20a%20tree%2C%20some%2050%20metres%20from%20the%20courtyard%2C%20to%20take%20cover%20but%20the%20drone%20followed%20us%20there%20and%20dropped%20an%20explosive.%20We%20started%20running%20again%20but%20we%20were%20thrown%20forward%20under%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20blast%20and%20were%20injured%20after%20hitting%20the%20ground%2C%26quot%3B%20Gambhir%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaoba%20Singh%2C%20a%20village%20volunteer%2C%20suspected%20that%20high-tech%20drones%20that%20can%20be%20used%20at%20night%20were%20brought%20from%20outside%20the%20country.%20Both%20Meiteis%20and%20Kukis%20have%20formed%20armed%20volunteer%20groups%20to%20protect%20their%20villages%20from%20attack%20by%20the%20other%20community.%20%26quot%3BIf%20sophisticated%20weapons%20can%20be%20sourced%20(from%20outside%20the%20country)%2C%20why%20can't%20high-tech%20drones%20that%20can%20be%20used%20in%20the%20dark%20be%20procured%20by%20those%20operating%20it%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20people%20injured%20in%20the%20bombings%20in%20Senjam%20Chirang%20are%20being%20treated%20in%20a%20private%20hospital%20in%20Imphal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20scared%20now%20and%20not%20staying%20at%20home%20even%20during%20the%20daytime.%20Around%2010%20families%20have%20taken%20refuge%20in%20a%20nearby%20community%20hall%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another%20villager%20W%20Inao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20government%20officer%20said%20that%20earlier%2C%20the%20trend%20was%20to%20buy%20drones%20from%20outside%20the%20state%2C%20but%20those%20were%20used%20for%20recreation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20outbreak%20of%20violence%2C%20drones%20have%20been%20used%20by%20the%20two%20warring%20groups%20for%20surveillance%20and%20tracking%20movement%20of%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20On%20whether%20the%20drones%20engaged%20in%20dropping%20bombs%20were%20purchased%20from%20outside%20the%20country%2C%20a%20central%20force%20official%20told%20PTI%20that%20only%20an%20expert%20can%20confirm%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20technical%20know-how%20or%20instruction%20from%20outside%20the%20state%2C%20a%20local%20militant%20cannot%20make%20improvised%20drones%20which%20can%20carry%20heavy%20payloads%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725469560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F1lqjs34_drone-manipur_625x300_02_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-villagers-terrified-by-drone-attacks-avoid-staying-at-home-6489984%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20section%20of%20villagers%20of%20Senjam%20Chirang%20in%20Manipur%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20abandon%20their%20homes%20and%20seek%20refuge%20in%20a%20nearby%20community%20hall%20after%20bombs%20dropped%20from%20a%20drone%20injured%20three%20members%20of%20a%20local%20resident's%20family%20two%20days%20ago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Asylum%20seeker%20who%20survived%20deadly%20boat%20sinking%20in%20Channel%20would%20risk%20his%20life%20again%20to%20reach%20UK%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725469380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F09%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-migrant-channel-refugee_6676709.jpg%3F20240904161008%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fasylum-seeker-who-survived-deadly-boat-sinking-in-channel-would-risk-his-life-again-to-reach-uk-13209700%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20asylum%20seeker%20who%20survived%20Tuesday's%20fatal%20small%20boat%20sinking%20in%20the%20Channel%20has%20told%20Sky%20News%20he%20would%20risk%20his%20life%20again%20to%20get%20to%20the%20UK.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A47%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fasylum-seeker-who-survived-deadly-boat-sinking-in-channel-would-risk-his-life-again-to-reach-uk