20detailed%20the%20brutal%20and%20inhumane%20torture%20before%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20being%20assaulted%20by%20Darshan%20and%20his%20gang%2C%20Renukaswamy's%20chest%20bones%20were%20broken.%20There%20are%20a%20total%20of%2039%20injury%20marks%20all%20over%20his%20body.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20deep%20cut%20on%20the%20victim's%20head%2C%E2%80%9D%20reads%20the%20chargesheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20the%20gang%20reportedly%20used%20a%20megger%20machine%2C%20an%20electrical%20device%20used%20to%20measure%20insulation%20resistance%2C%20to%20deliver%20electric%20shocks%20to%20Renukaswamy's%20private%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDarshan%20and%20his%20gang%20used%20the%20megger%20device%20to%20damage%20Renukaswamy's%20testicle%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20chargesheet%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20source%20said%20that%20Renukaswamy%20endured%20unheard-of%20and%20inhuman%20torture%20before%20being%20hacked%20to%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20committing%20the%20murder%2C%20Darshan%20and%20the%20other%20accused%20used%20their%20influence%20and%20money%20to%20dispose%20of%20the%20body%20and%20attempted%20to%20destroy%20evidence.%20They%20also%20tried%20to%20frame%20other%20individuals%20to%20escape%20charges%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20chargesheet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20with%20the%20common%20intention%20of%20committing%20the%20crime%2C%20they%20destroyed%20physical%2C%20technical%2C%20and%20scientific%20evidence%20and%20attempted%20to%20destroy%20further%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDarshan%20is%20named%20as%20the%20second%20accused%20in%20the%20case%2C%20and%20his%20legal%20team%20is%20preparing%20to%20submit%20a%20bail%20plea.%20However%2C%20police%20sources%20said%20that%20since%20he%20is%20booked%20in%20three%20new%20cases%20related%20to%20luxury%20treatment%20inside%20the%20prison%2C%20obtaining%20bail%20will%20not%20be%20an%20easy%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20found%20traces%20of%20Renukaswamy's%20blood%20on%20the%20clothes%20seized%20from%20Darshan.%20They%20also%20retrieved%20messages%20sent%20by%20his%20associates%20during%20the%20kidnapping%2C%20confinement%2C%20torture%2C%20murder%2C%20and%20disposal%20of%20Renukaswamy's%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20incident%2C%20Darshan%20had%20gone%20to%20Mysuru%20for%20the%20shoot%20of%20his%20upcoming%20movie%2C%20%E2%80%9CDevil.%E2%80%9D%20A%20team%20from%20Bengaluru%20Police%2C%20headed%20by%20ACP%20Chandan%20Kumar%2C%20arrested%20him%20in%20a%20hotel%20after%20cracking%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20Darshan%20tried%20to%20resist%20the%20arrest.%20However%2C%20ACP%20Chandan%20Kumar%20ordered%20him%20to%20get%20into%20the%20police%20jeep%20or%20face%20being%20dragged%20in%2C%20with%20further%20strong%20action%20as%20per%20the%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDarshan%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20superstars%20in%20the%20Kannada%20film%20industry.%20The%20budding%20industry%2C%20which%20had%20started%20to%20make%20its%20mark%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20has%20suffered%20a%20significant%20setback%20in%20light%20of%20these%20developments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20chargesheet%2C%20Pavithra%20Gowda%20is%20labelled%20as%20A-1%2C%20and%20Darshan%20as%20A-2.%20Fourteen%20individuals%20have%20been%20charged%20with%20murder%2C%20and%2014%20others%20face%20charges%20of%20abduction%20and%20murder.%20Karthik%20alias%20Kappe%2C%20Keshavamurthy%2C%20and%20Nikhil%20Nayak%20are%20charged%20with%20destruction%20of%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20volume%20contains%20a%20summary%20report%20of%20the%20case.%20The%20second%20volume%20comprises%20voluntary%20statements%20of%2017%20accused%20individuals.%20Volume%20number%20three%20has%20details%20of%20evidence%20both%20direct%20and%20circumstantial.%20The%20fourth%20volume%20has%20the%20post-mortem%20and%20Forensic%20Science%20Laboratory%20(FSL)%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fifth%20volume%20contains%20the%20FSL%20and%20CSFL%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20after%20the%20receipt%20of%20the%20chargesheet%20copies%20to%20all%20the%20accused%20persons%2C%20the%2024th%20ACMM%20court%20will%20commit%20the%20case%20and%20transfer%20it%20to%20the%20sessions%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725464700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fnc0o4c1o_darshan-ians-_625x300_04_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fk-taka-renukaswamy-s-testicle-damaged-with-megger-chargesheet-details-brutal-torture-6489790%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Karnataka%20Police%20submitted%20the%20chargesheet%20in%20the%20sensational%20kidnap%20and%20murder%20case%20of%20Renukaswamy%20which%20has%20established%20the%20role%20of%20jailed%20Kannada%20superstar%20Darshan%20and%20also%20detailed%20the%20brutal%20and%20inhumane%20torture%20before%20his%20death.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ICRA%20upgrades%20Vedanta's%20long-term%20rating%20to%20AA%20on%20strong%20credit%20profile%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725464685000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-06%2F20%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1718874489-5444.JPG%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ficra-upgrades-vedanta-s-long-term-rating-to-aa-on-strong-credit-profile-124090401182_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Credit%20rating%20agency%20ICRA%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20that%20it%20has%20upgraded%20Vedanta%20Ltd's%20long-term%20credit%20rating%2C%20reflecting%20the%20company's%20strengthened%20credit%20profile.%22%2C%22a