C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113068347.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EWilliam%20Bryan%2C%20a%2070-year-old%20from%20Alabama%2C%20tragically%20died%20during%20surgery%20in%20Florida%20after%20a%20surgeon%20mistakenly%20removed%20his%20liver%20instead%20of%20his%20spleen.%20This%20grave%20error%20caused%20immediate%20and%20catastrophic%20blood%20loss.%20His%20widow%20is%20now%20pursuing%20both%20civil%20and%20criminal%20proceedings%20against%20the%20surgeon%20and%20hospital%20involved%20in%20the%20incident.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Falabama-man-dies-after-florida-surgeon-mistakenly-removes-liver-instead-of-spleen%2Farticleshow%2F113068347.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Falabama-man-dies-after-florida-surgeon-mistakenly-removes-liver-instead-of-spleen%2Famp_articleshow%2F113068347.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Falabama-man-dies-after-florida-surgeon-mistakenly-removes-liver-instead-of-spleen%2Famp_articleshow%2F113068347.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nitin%20Gadkari%20Identifies%20%26quot%3BCulprits%26quot%3B%20Behind%20Shoddy%20Infra%20Projects%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20has%20strongly%20criticised%20those%20who%20draw%20up%20reports%20for%20building%20critical%20highways%20and%20tunnels%20across%20the%20country%20for%20not%20following%20proper%20procedures%2C%20which%20can%20lead%20to%20accidents%20and%20tunnel%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20should%20not%20use%20these%20words%2C%20but%20if%20there%20is%20any%20culprit%20in%20this%2C%20then%20it%20is%20the%20one%20who%20made%20the%20DPR.%20I%20apologise%3B%20I%20am%20using%20the%20word%20culprit.%20The%20companies%20that%20make%20DPRs%20are%20owned%20by%20retired%20government%20officers.%20They%20work%20on%20Google%20from%20their%20homes%20without%20any%20detailed%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20Minister%20said%20at%20the%202nd%20edition%20of%20'Tunnelling%20India'%20organised%20by%20the%20industry%20body%20FICCI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20detailed%20project%20report%2C%20or%20DPR%2C%20is%20a%20summary%20of%20key%20elements%20of%20any%20large%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gadkari%20said%20it%20is%20very%20important%20for%20DPR-makers%20to%20stick%20to%20proper%20procedures%20since%20the%20DPR%20contains%20a%20lot%20of%20technical%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20government%20has%20such%20a%20system%20that%20after%20getting%20the%20DPR%2C%20they%20only%20do%20the%20work%20of%20issuing%20the%20tender.%20Because%20the%20ministers%20are%20not%20the%20ones%20to%20understand%20technical%20terms%2C%20technical%20and%20financial%20qualifications%20are%20also%20wisely%20included%20by%20the%20officials%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Minister%20cautioned%20that%20some%20companies%20manipulate%20the%20tender%20process%2C%20which%20brings%20in%20risks%20of%20errors%20in%20the%20final%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20hesitation%20in%20saying%20that%20some%20big%20companies%20get%20these%20financial%20and%20technical%20qualifications%20done%20as%20per%20their%20own%20calculation%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gadkari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20manipulation%20in%20the%20tender%20process%20leads%20to%20cost%20escalation.%20One%20way%20to%20counter%20this%20tendency%20is%20to%20ensure%20healthy%20competition%20and%20carry%20out%20comprehensive%20studies%2C%20he%20added%2C%20citing%20as%20an%20example%20the%20efficient%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20Zozila%20tunnel%20was%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gadkari%20said%20government%20officers%20have%20a%20major%20influence%20in%20the%20decision-making%20process.%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20that%20we%20run%20the%20government...%20our%20joint%20secretary%2C%20undersecretary%20are%20guides%20and%20philosophers.%20And%20whatever%20they%20write%20on%20the%20file%20is%20signed%20by%20the%20Director%20General%2C%20and%20the%20minister%20also%20signs%20it%20in%20the%20same%20manner.%20This%20is%20how%20our%20Ram%20Rajya%20runs%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gadkari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725459120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fhkd2t4o8_nitin-gadkari_625x300_04_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitin-gadkari-identifies-culprits-behind-shoddy-infra-projects-6490574%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Minister%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20has%20strongly%20criticised%20those%20who%20draw%20up%20reports%20for%20building%20critical%20highways%20and%20tunnels%20across%20the%20country%20for%20not%20following%20proper%20procedures%2C%20which%20can%20lead%20to%20accidents%20and%20tunnel%20collapse.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitin-gadkari-identifies-culprits-behind-shoddy-infra-projects-6490574%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dr%20Reddy's%2C%20Lupin%20recall%20products%20in%20US%20due%20to%20manufacturing%20issues%3A%20USFDA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725458805000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-05%2F27%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1716827729-862.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fdr-reddy-s-lupin-recall-products-in-us-due-to-manufacturing-issues-usfda-124090400721_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Results%20for%20unknown%20impurity%20were%200.13%20per%20cent%20and%200.11%20per%20cent%2C%20respectively%2C%20exceeding%20the%200.10%20per%20cent%20specification%20limit%2C%20USFDA%20noted%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fdr-reddy-s-lupin-recall-products-in-us-due-to-manufacturing-issues-usfda-124090400721_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fdr-reddy-s-lupin-recall-products-in-us-due-to-manufacturing-issues-usfda-124090400721_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fdr-reddy-s-lupin-recall-products-in-us-due-to-manufacturing-issues-usfda-124090400721_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rahul%20More%20Intellectual%2C%20Strategist%20Compared%20To%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%3A%20Sam%20Pitroda%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20is%20more%20intellectual%20and%20more%20of%20a%20strategist%20as%20compared%20with%20his%20father%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20says%20long-time%20Gandhi%20family%20confidant%20Sam%20Pitroda%2C%20describing%20both%20leaders%20as%20%26quot%3Bcustodians%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20PTI%2C%20Mr%20Pitroda%20also%20asserted%20that%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20all%20the%20qualities%20of%20a%20future%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pitroda%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Indian%20Overseas%20Congress%2C%20dismissed%20as%20%26quot%3Bbogus%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP's%20attack%20on%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20the%20past%20over%20his%20remarks%20critical%20of%20the%20government%20during%20his%20visits%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20upcoming%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20next%20week%2C%20Mr%20Pitroda%20said%20he%20is%20not%20coming%20to%20the%20US%20in%20his%20official%20capacity%20but%20will%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20interact%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20people%20on%20Capitol%20Hill%20at%20an%20%26quot%3Bindividual%20level%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Gandhi)%20will%20definitely%20have%20interactions%20with%20the%20press%20at%20the%20national%20press%20club%2C%20he%20will%20meet%20with%20the%20think%20tank%20people%20and%20will%20also%20have%20interaction%20at%20Georgetown%20University%20which%20is%20equally%20important%20in%20Washington%20DC%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Indian%20Overseas%20Congress%20chief%20said%20of%20Gandhi's%20first%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20since%20assuming%20the%20mantle%20of%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20will%20visit%20the%20US%20from%20September%208-10%20during%20which%20he%20will%20hold%20numerous%20interactions%20in%20Washington%20DC%20and%20Dallas%2C%20including%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Georgetown%20and%20the%20University%20of%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20similarities%20and%20divergences%20between%20former%20prime%20minister%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Pitroda%20said%20he%20had%20worked%20with%20a%20number%20of%20prime%20ministers%20closely%20such%20as%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20PV%20Narasimha%20Rao%2C%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20VP%20Singh%2C%20Chandra%20Sekhar%20and%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20an%20opportunity%20to%20see%20many%20prime%20ministers%20from%20very%20close%20quarters%20but%20the%20difference%20between%20Rahul%20and%20Rajiv%20maybe%20is%20that%20Rahul%20is%20much%20more%20intellectual%2C%20thinker%2C%20Rajiv%20was%20a%20little%20more%20doer.%20They%20have%20the%20same%20DNA%2C%20they%20have%20the%20same%20concerns%20and%20feelings%20for%20the%20people%2C%20they%20genuinely%20believe%20in%20building%20a%20better%20India%20for%20everybody%2C%20they%20are%20genuinely%20simple%20people.%20They%20don't%20have%20big%20personal%20needs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20leader%20told%20PTI%20from%20Chicago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRahul%20is%20a%20strategist%20more%20so%20than%20Rajiv%20was.%20They%20are%20products%20of%20different%20times%2C%20different%20tools%2C%20and%20different%20experiences.%20Poor%20Rahul%20has%20gone%20through%20two%20big%20shocks%20in%20life%2C%20(death%20of)%20his%20grandmother%20and%20his%20father.%20So%20they%20have%20had%20different%20paths%20to%20travel%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20fundamentals%20are%20clear%2C%20both%20are%20%26quot%3Bcustodians%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20India%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20had%20laid%20out%20and%20every%20leader%20of%20the%20party%20believed%20in%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNarasimha%20Rao%20believed%20in%20it%2C%20(Mallikarjun)%20Kharge%20ji%20believes%20in%20it%20and%20collectively%20it%20is%20our%20job%20to%20build%20the%20India%20our%20founding%20fathers%20had%20envisaged%2C%26quot%3B%20Pitroda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20image%20is%20finally%20coming%20through%20the%20way%20he%20is%20and%20the%20two%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatras%20had%20helped%20in%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%20of%20all%2C%20the%20image%20created%20in%20the%20media%20was%20based%20on%20a%20well-orchestrated%20campaign%20against%20an%20individual%20where%20millions%20and%20millions%20of%20dollars%20were%20spent%20on%20maligning%20this%20young%20man%20and%20when%20he%20is%20highly%20educated%2C%20people%20said%20he%20never%20went%20to%20college.%20People%20created%20this%20image%20by%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20It%20was%20a%20false%20image.%20I%20give%20a%20lot%20of%20credit%20to%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20for%20standing%20up%20and%20fighting%20it%20for%20a%20long%20time%20and%20surviving%2C%20nobody%20else%20would%20have%20been%20able%20to%20survive%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pitroda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20onslaught%20day%20in%20and%20day%20out%20on%20an%20individual%2C%20his%20family%2C%20his%20legacy%2C%20his%20party%20character%2C%20it%20is%20bad.%20These%20are%20mean%20people%20who%20by%20design%20lie%2C%20cheat%20and%20say%20all%20kinds%20of%20things%20about%20individuals.%20I%20have%20seen%20that%20in%20my%20case%20also%20to%20a%20very%20small%20extent%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2082-year-old%20technocrat%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPitroda%20said%20things%20have%20turned%20around%20in%20the%20public's%20mind%20because%20they%20are%20beginning%20to%20realise%20that%20the%20media%20is%20controlled%2C%20messages%20are%20designed%20to%20hurt%20people%20and%20lies%20are%20finally%20catching%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20cannot%20lie%20all%20the%20time%20to%20the%20people.%20People%20are%20now%20beginning%20to%20see%20that%20it%20was%20said%20'we%20will%20create%2020%20million%20jobs'%2C%20but%20they%20haven't%20done%20that%2C%20it%20was%20said%20black%20money%20will%20be%20brought%20back%2C%20it%20hasn't%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20whether%20he%20sees%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20as%20a%20future%20PM%2C%20Pitroda%20said%20that%20is%20for%20the%20people%20to%20decide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20my%20personal%20experience%20and%20I%20may%20be%20biased%2C%20I%20think%20he%20is%20very%20capable.%20He%20is%20a%20decent%20human%20being%2C%20he%20is%20well%20educated%2C%20he%20has%20the%20right%20DNA%20and%20I%20see%20him%20as%20the%20custodian%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20democracy%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20always%20promoted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20Congress%20leaders'%20view%20that%20Gandhi%20had%20earned%20the%20right%20to%20assume%20the%20post%20of%20PM%20when%20the%20Congress%20comes%20to%20power%2C%20Pitroda%20said%20he%20agrees%20with%20the%20view%20but%20ultimately%20it%20is%20for%20the%20party%20to%20decide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20whether%20he%20sees%20qualities%20of%20a%20future%20PM%20in%20Mr%20Gandhi%2C%20Mr%20Pitroda%20emphatically%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAbsolutely%2C%20no%20question%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%20Asked%20about%20the%20attack%20his%20party%20and%20he%20faced%20from%20the%20BJP%20during%20the%20past%20foreign%20visits%20of%20Gandhi%20over%20his%20critical%20remarks%2C%20Pitroda%20said%20that%20in%20this%20day%20and%20age%20when%20communication%20is%20instant%20and%20distance%20is%20dead%2C%20there%20are%20no%20local%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20local%20event%20becomes%20a%20global%20event%2C%20a%20church%20burn%20in%20France%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20French%20event%2C%20it%20is%20a%20global%20event%20as%20an%20example.%20Same%20with%20wars.%20So%20it%20is%20wrong%20to%20assume%20that%20there%20are%20certain%20things%20you%20say%20at%20home%20and%20there%20are%20certain%20things%20you%20say%20abroad%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCriticising%20the%20government%20is%20not%20criticising%20India.%20It%20is%20ok%20to%20criticise%20the%20government%20by%20an%20opposition%20leader%2C%20That%20is%20his%20job%20in%20fact%2C%20so%20why%20complain%3F%20I%20think%20this%20whole%20business%20of%20criticising%20abroad%20is%20bogus%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Indian%20Overseas%20Congress%20chairman%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20June%204%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20results%20and%20its%20significance%2C%20Pitroda%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20election%20the%20fear%20was%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20get%20400%20seats.%20Then%20it%20would%20have%20been%20an%20absolute%20majority%20which%20could%20bring%20about%20in%20the%20judgement%20of%20many%20people%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20concern%20at%20various%20levels%20on%20the%20Constitution%2C%20authoritarian%20mindset%20and%20more%20attack%20on%20the%20opposition%20and%20media.%20So%20this%20election%20was%20very%20important%20because%20the%20BJP%20could%20be%20brought%20down%20to%20240%20seats.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20message%20is%20loud%20and%20clear%20that%20ordinary%20people%20of%20India%20prefer%20democracy%2C%20Constitution%2C%20freedom%20and%20justice%2C%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%