20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F91n3627g_kandahar_625x300_04_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(In%20light%20of%20the%20controversy%20over%20the%20Netflix%20series%20'IC%20814%3A%20The%20Kandahar%20Hijack'%2C%20here%20is%20a%20view%20on%20the%201999%20hijack%20and%20its%20aftermath.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-ic-814-whats-in-a-name-just-a-reason-to-outrage-6489378%5C%22%3EClick%20here%20to%20read%20Nishtha%20Gautam's%20counterview%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20late%20evening%20wind%20chill%20on%20December%2031%2C%201999%2C%20caused%20considerable%20discomfort%20for%20everyone%20gathered%20at%20Indira%20Gandhi%20International%20Airport%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Braving%20the%20cold%20were%20the%20relatives%20of%20the%20recently%20freed%20passengers%2C%20media%20personnel%2C%20curious%20locals%20from%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%2C%20numerous%20security%20personnel%2C%20and%20logistical%20staff%20from%20various%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arrival%20of%20an%20Indian%20Airlines%20plane%20elicited%20cheers.%20Suddenly%2C%20the%20crowd%20seemed%20to%20forget%20the%20tragic%20killing%20of%20Rupin%20Katyal%20and%20the%20muted%20anger%20over%20the%20release%20of%20three%20notorious%20terrorists-Masood%20Azhar%2C%20Mushtaq%20Zargar%2C%20and%20Omar%20Shaikh-in%20exchange%20for%20the%20hostages%20aboard%20the%20hijacked%20Indian%20Airlines%20IC814%20flight%20from%20Kathmandu%20to%20New%20Delhi.%20The%20excitement%20to%20see%20the%20passengers%20return%20home%20safely%20overshadowed%20all%20other%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20passengers%20began%20to%20disembark%2C%20media%20personnel%20focused%20on%20two%20main%20aspects%3A%20the%20trauma%20and%20suffering%20endured%20by%20the%20hostages%2C%20and%20the%20identities%20of%20the%20hijackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EChief%2C%20Doctor%2C%20Burger%2C%20Bhola%2C%20And%20Shankar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20morning%2C%20the%20pseudonyms%20or%20call%20signs%20used%20by%20the%20five%20hijackers%20-%20Chief%2C%20Doctor%2C%20Burger%2C%20Bhola%2C%20and%20Shankar%20-%20were%20widely%20reported%20in%20newspapers.%20With%20the%20real%20identities%20of%20the%20hijackers%20still%20undisclosed%2C%20the%20public%20dissemination%20of%20these%20pseudonyms%20heightened%20anxiety%20and%20tension%20for%20the%20then%20Vajpayee%20government.%20Rumours%2C%20particularly%20from%20across%20the%20border%2C%20suggesting%20that%20some%20hijackers%20were%20Kashmiri%20Hindus%2C%20exacerbated%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20the%20Mumbai%20Police%2C%20in%20close%20cooperation%20with%20central%20intelligence%20agencies%2C%20apprehended%20four%20Harkat-ul-Ansar%2FMujahideen%20operatives-Mohammed%20Rehan%2C%20Mohammed%20Iqbal%2C%20Yasuf%20Nepali%2C%20and%20Abdul%20Latif-who%20had%20supported%20the%20hijackers.%20Rehan%20hailed%20from%20Karachi%2C%20Iqbal%20from%20Multan%2C%20Yusuf%20was%20reportedly%20a%20Nepali%20national%2C%20and%20Latif%20was%20an%20Indian%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20reportedly%20recruited%20by%20Pakistan%20ISI%20during%20his%20time%20in%20the%20Gulf%20Region%20and%20later%20trained%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20interrogation%2C%20these%20operatives%20revealed%20the%20real%20identities%20of%20all%20the%20hijackers.%20This%20prompted%20the%20then%20Home%20Minister%2C%20L.K.%20Advani%2C%20to%20issue%20a%20detailed%20public%20statement%20about%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20hijack%2C%20the%20evidence%20linking%20them%20to%20Pakistan%20and%20its%20notorious%20ISI%20to%20relay%20this%20information%20globally.%20The%20statement%20identified%20Ibrahim%20Athar%20from%20Bahawalpur%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20as%20'Chief'%3B%20Shahid%20Akhtar%20Sayed%20Gulshan%20Iqbal%2C%20Sunny%20Ahmed%20Qazi%20and%20Mistri%20Zahoor%20Ibrahim%2C%20all%20from%20Karachi%2C%20as%20'Doctor'%2C%20'Burger'%20and%20'Bhola'%2C%20respectively%3B%20and%20Shakir%20from%20Sukkur%20as%20'Shankar'.%20The%20names%20and%20places%20of%20origin%20of%20the%20hijackers%20were%20provided%20to%20dispel%20any%20misgivings%20about%20them%20that%20may%20have%20been%20there%20for%20the%20past%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20over%2024%20years%2C%20the%20release%20of%20a%20series%20on%20the%20IC%20814%20Kandahar%20hijack%20has%20revived%20these%20memories%20and%20controversies%2C%20particularly%20surrounding%20the%20names%20of%20the%20hijackers%20-%20Bhola%20and%20Shankar%20-%20which%20has%20sparked%20a%20passionate%20public%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20mainly%20focused%20on%20two%20issues%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Intent%20Of%20the%20series%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIs%20there%20malicious%20intent%20by%20the%20producer%20and%20director%20to%20craft%20a%20narrative%20that%20exonerates%20Pakistan%20and%20the%20ISI%2C%20while%20placing%20all%20blame%20on%20Osama%20bin%20Laden's%20Al-Qaeda%20and%20Afghanistan%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20question%20arose%20because%20Osama%20bin%20Laden%20and%20Al-Qaeda's%20direct%20involvement%20was%20not%20discussed%20in%20detail%20by%20those%20at%20the%20helm%20then.%20It's%20true%20that%20Laden%20was%20living%20in%20Afghanistan%20and%20was%20one%20of%20the%20principal%20players%20in%20the%20state%20of%20affairs%20there.%20There%20were%20scenes%20of%20jubilation%20immediately%20after%20the%20landing%20and%20release%20of%20three%20terrorists%20by%20Indian%20authorities.%20But%20that%20Laden%20or%20his%20group%20masterminded%20the%20hijack%20had%20not%20been%20under%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20released%20terrorists%20soon%20returned%20to%20Pakistan%20to%20get%20a%20hero%20welcome%2C%20formed%20terror%20outfits%20and%20used%20Pakistan's%20soil%20to%20indulge%20in%20terror%20activities%20or%20export%20terrorism%20from%20there%20-%20further%20proof%20of%20the%20country's%20direct%20complicity%20in%20the%20crime.%20The%20series%2C%20however%2C%20has%20characters%20playing%20leads%20in%20intelligence%20agencies%20and%20shows%20how%20ISI%20couldn't%20have%20been%20connected%20with%20the%20hijackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Misleading%20Names%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDid%20the%20series%20mislead%20viewers%20by%20using%20names%20like%20Bhola%20and%20Shankar%2C%20thereby%20causing%20confusion%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20issued%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Monika%20Shergill%2C%20Vice%20President%2C%20Content%2C%20Netflix%20India%2C%20after%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20OTT%20platform's%20representatives%20with%20the%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20Ministry%2C%20clears%20the%20air%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20benefit%20of%20audiences%20unfamiliar%20with%20the%201999%20hijacking%20of%20Indian%20Airlines%20Flight%20814%2C%20the%20opening%20disclaimer%20has%20been%20updated%20to%20include%20the%20real%20and%20code%20names%20of%20the%20hijackers.%20The%20code%20names%20in%20the%20series%20reflect%20those%20used%20during%20the%20actual%20event.%20India%20has%20a%20rich%20culture%20of%20storytelling%20-%20and%20we%20are%20committed%20to%20showcasing%20these%20stories%20and%20their%20authentic%20representation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%20The%20statement%20gives%20a%20sense%20that%20the%20platform%20realised%20that%20it%20was%20perhaps%20a%20mistake%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20makers%20not%20to%20give%20the%20real%20identities%20of%20the%20five%20hijackers%20at%20any%20point%20in%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20series%20portrays%20Jaswant%20Singh%2C%20the%20then%20external%20affairs%20minister%2C%20as%20the%20one%20who%20was%20taking%20all%20the%20calls.%20The%20real%20story%20is%20slightly%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Netflix%20agreeing%20to%20make%20amendments%2C%20at%20least%20the%20ferocity%20of%20the%20controversy%20subsides%20for%20now.%20It%20is%20the%20second%20time%20a%20major%20OTT%20platform%20has%20agreed%20to%20make%20changes%20after%20the%20ministry%20took%20up%20the%20issue%20with%20them.%20In%20January%202021%2C%20on%20the%20ministry's%20intervention%2C%20Amazon%20Prime%20made%20some%20changes%20to%20the%20series%20%3Cem%3ETandav%3C%2Fem%3E.%20But%20then%20there%20is%20a%20difference%20-%20Tandav%20was%20fiction%2C%20while%3Cem%3E%20IC814%3A%20The%20Kandahar%20Hijack%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20based%20on%20a%20real%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Sanjay%20Singh%20is%20Contributing%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725452520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F4pk6fti_knadahar_625x300_04_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Freal-vs-reel-here-is-how-the-1999-hijack-really-played-out-6489281%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20the%20second%20time%20a%20major%20OTT%20platform%20has%20agreed%20to%20make%20changes%20after%20the%20ministry%20took%20up%20the%20issue%20with%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Freal-vs-reel-here-is-how-the-1999-hijack-really-played-out-6489281%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20IC%20814%20Row%3A%20What's%20In%20A%20Name%3F%20Just%20A%20Reason%20To%20Outrage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fem5p4068_ic-814_625x300_04_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(In%20light%20of%20the%20controversy%20over%20the%20Netflix%20series%20'IC%20814%3A%20The%20Kandahar%20Hijack'%2C%20here