2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Internet%20has%20been%2C%20predictably%2C%20awash%20with%20angry%20responses%20to%20the%20series%20using%20these%20codenames.%20It%20is%20the%20same%20people%20who%20are%20upset%20that%20Muslim%20actors%2C%20artists%2C%20et%20al%2C%20use%20%26quot%3BHindu%26quot%3B%20names%20for%20popularity.%20This%20entire%20'controversy'%20could%20have%20easily%20been%20ignored%20had%20it%20not%20led%20to%20top-down%20interventions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERIP%2C%20freedom%20of%20speech%2C%20expression%2C%20and%20everything%20else%20with%20it%20when%20even%20the%20facts%20have%20to%20surrender%20to%20sentiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20here%20is%20the%20bigger%20question%20about%20names-what%20is%2C%20indeed%2C%20in%20a%20name%3F%20The%20recent%20outrage%20is%20in%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20the%20situation%20when%20many%20clapped%20enthusiastically%20in%20the%20cinema%20halls%20when%20Siddharth%20Malhotra%20played%20Captain%20Vikram%20Batra%2C%20the%20hero%20of%20the%20Kargil%20war%2C%20fought%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20barely%20six%20months%20before%20IC-814%20was%20hijacked.%20Captain%20Batra%2C%20before%20he%20was%20killed%20in%20action%2C%20went%20by%20an%20alias%20Shershah.%20Now%20think%20about%20Iftikhar%2C%20another%20film%2C%20another%20alias%20used%20by%20an%20army%20officer%2C%20Maj%20Mohit%20Sharma.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20People%20Take%20Aliases%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20norm%2C%20not%20an%20aberration%2C%20for%20Indian%20armed%20forces%20personnel%20to%20use%20aliases%20during%20counter-insurgency%20and%20conflict%20situations.%20Their%20identity%20becomes%20the%20Trojan%20horse%20to%20infiltrate%20and%20destroy%20the%20enemy's%20defences.%20This%20is%20precisely%20what%20the%20enemy%20does%2C%20too.%20The%20entire%20breadth%20of%20tactical%20communication%20is%20predicated%20on%20aliases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcluding%20a%20study%20to%20assess%20%26quot%3Bimplicit%20and%20explicit%20attitudes%20toward%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20within%20a%20predominantly%20Christian%20sample%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%26quot%3B%20juxtaposing%20names%20with%20adjectives%2C%20researchers%20Wade%20C.%20Rowatt%2C%20Lewis%20M.%20Franklin%20and%20Marla%20Cotton%20stated%20in%202005%2C%20%26quot%3Bself-reported%20attitudes%20toward%20Christians%20were%20more%20positive%20than%20their%20self-reported%20attitudes%20towards%20Muslims%26quot%3B.%20This%20is%20consistent%20with%20social%20identity%20theory.%20The%20findings%20of%20any%20such%20study%20are%20going%20to%20be%20similar%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmed%20forces%20personnel%20engaging%20in%20covert%20operations%20know%20it%20is%20easier%20to%20blend%20in%20when%20your%20name%20does%20not%20have%20unpleasant%20associations.%20And%20so%20do%20terrorists.%20The%20only%20people%20ignoring%20it%20are%20the%20frenzied%20internet%20warriors.%20But%20that's%20not%20surprising.%20The%20name%20'conspiracy'%20is%20just%20another%20quick-to-find%20trigger.%20This%20time%2C%20however%2C%20the%20trigger%20probably%20masks%20a%20sense%20of%20institutional%20shame.%20The%20fact%20that%20Masood%20Azhar%20is%20still%20free%20and%20conveniently%20plotting%20and%20carrying%20out%20terrorist%20actions%20against%20India%20is%20an%20injury%20to%20the%20insult%20that%20the%20IC-814%20hijacking%20was.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Should%20Really%20Rattle%20Us%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20truly%20merits%20outrage%20is%20how%20the%20systems%20disallowed%20a%20timely%20follow-up%20on%20multiple%20intelligence%20warnings.%20Let's%20outrage%20how%2C%20despite%20endless%20domestic%20brouhaha%20over%20the%20role%20of%20Pakistan%20in%20the%20hijacking%2C%20we%20are%20yet%20to%20mount%20any%20case%20against%20the%20inter-services%20intelligence%20(ISI)%20agency%20in%20a%20global%20forum.%20Let%20us%20also%20express%20our%20outrage%2C%20since%20we%20are%20tireless%2C%20about%20how%20our%20security%20infrastructure%20has%20a%20thousand%20leaks%2C%20ensuring%20no%20timely%20action%20could%20be%20taken%20before%20the%20flight%20took%20off%2C%20first%20from%20Kathmandu%20and%20later%20from%20Amritsar.%20As%20senior%20police%20officer%20KPS%20Gill%20noted%20in%20his%20assessment%20of%20the%20event%2C%20even%20the%20telephone%20numbers%20of%20the%20Crisis%20Management%20Group%20listed%20at%20the%20Delhi%20Airport%20were%20incorrect.%20Let's%20outrage%20for%20accountability%20and%20systemic%20overhaul.%20Let's%20outrage%20because%20we%20do%20not%20have%20any%20coherent%20strategy%20to%20deal%20with%20our%20enemies%2C%20so%20we%20only%20either%20respond%20to%20the%20stimuli%20or%20busy%20ourselves%20fighting%20strawmen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20outrage%20will%20not%20happen%20simply%20because%20it%20does%20not%20suit%20the%20narrative.%20Calling%20names%20and%20calling%20out%20for%20names%20are%20easier%20when%20faced%20with%20uncomfortable%20truths.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Nishtha%20Gautam%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20author%20and%20academic.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725451860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F4qj3ne88_ic-814_625x300_04_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-ic-814-whats-in-a-name-just-a-reason-to-outrage-6489378%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20truly%20merits%20outrage%20is%20how%20the%20systems%20disallowed%20a%20timely%20follow-up%20on%20multiple%20intelligence%20warnings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-ic-814-whats-in-a-name-just-a-reason-to-outrage-6489378%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Statehood%20And%20Ties%20Of%20Blood%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Election%20Pitch%20In%20J%26amp%3BK%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAiming%20to%20win%20over%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20ahead%20of%20the%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20which%20begin%20in%20less%20than%20two%20weeks%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20opted%20to%20mix%20a%20political%20pitch%20with%20an%20emotional%20one%20while%20kicking%20off%20his%20party's%20campaign%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%20on%20Wednesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20sees%20its%20first%20election%20in%20nearly%2010%20years%20as%20well%20as%20its%20first%20as%20a%20Union%20Territory%20after%20it%20was%20stripped%20of%20its%20special%20status%20under%20Article%20370%20in%202019%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20made%20the%20restoration%20of%20statehood%20the%20central%20plank%20of%20his%20addresses%20on%20Wednesday%20while%20also%20reminding%20people%20of%20the%20ties%20of%20blood%20he%20and%20his%20family%20share%20with%20them%2C%20going%20as%20far%20back%20as%20his%20great-grandfather%20and%20India's%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20is%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20also%20took%20a%20jibe%20at%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20-%20and%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20through%20him%20-%20by%20calling%20him%20a%20'%3Cem%3Eraja%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(king).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20will%20see%20its%20campaign%20begin%20on%20Friday%20with%20rallies%20being%20addressed%20by%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20hit%20back%20and%20accused%20the%20Congress-National%20Conference%20alliance%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20being%20supported%20by%20militants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Kings%20Removed'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20rally%20for%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20from%20Dooru%2C%20Ghulam%20Ahmad%20Mir%2C%20with%20National%20Conference%20chief%20Farooq%20Abdullah%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20cited%20several%20decisions%20that%20had%20to%20be%20rolled%20back%20by%20the%20Centre%20and%20cited%20that%20as%20proof%20of%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance's%20growing%20strength%20in%20the%20country.%20This%20strength%2C%20he%20told%20his%20audience%2C%20would%20ensure%20that%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20would%20be%20granted%20statehood%20if%20the%20people%20voted%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20into%20power%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%201947%2C%20we%20removed%20the%20kings%20and%20formed%20a%20democratic%20government.%20We%20gave%20the%20country%20a%20Constitution.%20But%20a%20%3Cem%3Eraja%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20ruling%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20today.%20His%20name%20is%20LG%20(lieutenant%20governor)%2C%20but%20he%20is%20a%20%3Cem%3Eraja%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Your%20money%20is%20being%20stolen%20and%20given%20to%20people%20from%20outside.%20Be%20that%20in%20the%20form%20of%20contracts%20or%20anything%20else...%20The%20first%20thing%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20is%20restoring%20statehood%20to%20J%26amp%3BK%20because%20it%20wasn't%20just%20your%20state%20that%20was%20snatched...%20Your%20rights%2C%20your%20wealth%2C%20all%20of%20it%20is%20being%20snatched%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPersonal%20Relationship%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20another%20rally%20in%20Anantnag%2C%20he%20spoke%20about%20the%20personal%20ties%20he%20has%20with%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20know%20that%20you%20and%20I%20have%20a%20blood%20relation.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20political%20relationship.%20Be%20it%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20or%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20it%20is%20an%20old%20relationship.%20Whatever%20you%20want%20from%20me%2C%20my%20doors%20are%20always%20open%20for%20you.%20I%20want%20to%20serve%20you%20in%20Parliament.%20I%20will%20raise%20your%20issues%2C%20your%20pain%20and%20your%20sorrow.%20The%20country%20needs%20to%20know%20that%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20in%20India's%20history%20that%20a%20state%20has%20become%20a%20Union%20Territory%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20used%20the%20Kashmiri%20Pandit%20issue%20for%20political%20reasons%20and%20has%20not%20helped%20the%20community.%20Using%20his%20oft-repeated%20'%3Cem%3Emohabbat%20ki%20dukaan%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(shop%20of%20love)%20phrase%2C%20he%20asserted%20that%20the%20Congress%20will%20stand%20with%20the%20community%20and%20work%20for%20its%20welfare%20if%20the%20party%20forms%20a%20government%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Difficult%20Time'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Conference%20is%20the%20senior%20partner%20of%20the%20alliance%20in%20the%20UT%2C%20contesting%2051%20of%2090%20Assembly%20seats%20against%20the%20Congress'%2032%20-%20with%20friendly%20fights%20in%20five%20constituencies%20-%20and%20party%20chief%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20said%20the%20coalition%20will%20be%20successful%20in%20the%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20raising%20our%20voice.%20This%20is%20a%20slap%20on%20the%20face%20of%20people%20who%20called%20us%20Pakistanis%2C%20Khalistanis%20and%20whatnot.%20I%20hope%20that%20the%20people%20of%20India%20will%20understand%20that%20we%20want%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20its%20people%20to%20prosper%20after%20the%20difficult%20time%20they%20have%20been%20through.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20a%20state%20has%20become%20a%20Union%20Territory.%20We%20need%20to%20change%20this%2C%20we%20want%20statehood%2C%20and%20that's%20what%20we%20are%20working%20towards%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20Hits%20Back%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScoffing%20at%20the%20remarks%20by%20Mr%20Gandhi%20and%20Mr%20Abdullah%2C%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Ram%20Madhav%20said%20the%20parties%20are%20being%20supported%20by%20militants.%20The%20BJP%20has%20consistently%20maintained%20that%20J%26amp%3BK%20has%20progressed%20after%20the%20removal%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20Mr%20Madhav%20claimed%20that%20the%20Congress%2C%20National%20Conference%20and%20Mehbooba%20Mufti's%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20(PDP)%20want%20to%20push%20the%20Union%20Territory%20off%20the%20path%20of%20development.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20remind%20the%20people%20that%20the%20manifestoes%20released%20by%20the%20National%20Conference%2C%20PDP%20and%20others%20want%20to%20take%20J%26amp%3BK%20back%20to%20the%20old%20days%20and%20old%20problems.%20They%20are%20openly%20taking%20the%20support%20of%20militants%20to%20fight%20the%20elections.%20I%20am%20seeing%20that%20former%20militants%20are%20supporting%2C%20and%20campaigning%20for%2C%20National%20Conference%20and%20PDP%20candidates.%20We%20have%20to%20defeat%20such%20parties.%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20will%20see%20a%20government%20being%20formed%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20will%20vote%20in%20three%20phases%20between%20September%2018%20and%20October%201.%20Counting%20will%20take%20place%20on%20October%208.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725450540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fbkjqu2c_rahul-gandhi-kashmir_625x300_04_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-election-jammu-and-kashmir-rahul-gandhi-statehood-and-ties-of-blood-rahul-gandhis-election-pitch-in-j-k-6489191%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aiming%20to%20win%20over%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20ahead%20of%20the%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20which%20begin%20in%20less%20than%20two%20weeks%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20opted%20to%20mix%20a%20political%20pitch%20with%20an%20emotional%20one%20while%20kicking%20off%20his%20party's%20campaign%20in%20the%20UT%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22e