ernment.%20For%20this%2C%20he%20has%20received%20constant%20support%20from%20his%20wife%2C%20a%20few%20fellow%20officers%20and%20old%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Famit-lathia-2-1724916794.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amit%20has%20been%20recognised%20for%20his%20work%20and%20continues%20to%20be%20an%20inspiration%20for%20hundreds%20of%20underprivileged%20children.%20%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Famit-lathia-2-1724916794.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Famit-lathia-2-1724916794-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Famit-lathia-2-1724916794-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Famit-lathia-2-1724916794-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Famit-lathia-2-1724916794-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-363347%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAmit%20has%20been%20recognised%20for%20his%20work%20and%20continues%20to%20be%20an%20inspiration%20for%20hundreds%20of%20underprivileged%20children.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20wife%E2%80%99s%20unwavering%20support%20and%20dedication%20to%20the%20cause%20have%20been%20instrumental%20in%20the%20success%20of%20his%20mission.%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20my%20wedding%2C%20I%20informed%20my%20wife%20Manju%20about%20my%20purpose.%20She%20also%20stepped%20in%20and%20vowed%20to%20help%20me%20in%20the%20cause.%20Today%2C%20Manju%20is%20a%20mathematics%20professor%20in%20a%20government%20college%20in%20Sonipat.%20She%20takes%20care%20of%20all%20of%20the%