during%20the%20races.%20A%20racer%20needs%20the%20physique%20of%20a%20fighter%20pilot%2C%20including%20quick%20reflexes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20Despite%20setbacks%20like%20crashes%20and%20spins%2C%20Salva%E2%80%99s%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F335635%2Fnarain-karthikeyan-india-first-f1-driver-entrepreneur-drivex-mobility-refurbished-two-wheelers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20passion%20and%20ability%20to%20learn%20from%20each%20experience%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehave%20kept%20her%20on%20track.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20as%20Salva%20prepares%20to%20join%20the%20Formula%201%20Academy%20in%20January%202025%2C%20she%20stands%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20history.%20Qualifying%20for%20the%20academy%20would%20not%20only%20alleviate%20her%20financial%20burdens%20but%20also%20cement%20her%20place%20in%20the%20global%20racing%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalva%E2%80%99s%20ultimate%20goal%20is%20clear%3A%20to%20represent%20India%20in%20Formula%201%20and%20inspire%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20female%20racers.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20female%20athlete%2C%20I%20am%20particularly%20motivated%20to%20challenge%20the%20norms%20and%20make%20a%20significant%20impact%20in%20a%20field%20that%20has%20historically%20been%20male-dominated%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fmagazines%2Fpanache%2Fmeet-25-yr-old-salva-marjan-keralas-first-woman-to-join-formula-1-racing-academy%2Farticleshow%2F112728519.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeet%2025-yr-old%20Salva%20Marjan%2C%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20first%20woman%20set%20to%20join%20Formula%201%20racing%20academy%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20by%20The%20Economic%20Times%2C%20Published%20on%2023%